**Create Domain**

To begin, enter the domain name for this new web site and specify the directory where the contents of this new web site will be in. Please be aware that the folder will not be automatically created for you.

- Go to https://www.serverpointapps.com/ , click on **Client Portal**.
- Click on the **Menu** , then go **Web Sites and Stats**
- On right top side, click on **New Website** button.
- Click on **Web Site** tab.
- Put domain name in the “Domain name” field and the root directory name in the “Directory folder” filed and click on “check sign” (ok) button

**Create Domain Pointer**

- Go to https://www.serverpointapps.com/ , click on Client Portal.
- Click on the Menu , then go Web Sites and Stats
- On right top side, click on New Website button..
- Click on Web Site tab.
- Put domain name in the “Domain name” field and in the field “Directory folder”, after public_html, do not add anything and it will be setup as pointer

**Create Sub Domains**

You can create a subdomain, of the form of sub.domain.com, for your primary site or any of your subwebsites. Please be aware that the folder will not be automatically created for you.

- Go to https://www.serverpointapps.com/ , click on Client Portal.
- Click on the Menu , then go Web Sites and Stats
- On right top side, click on New Website button.
- Click on Subdomains tab.
- Put sub-domain name in the “Subdomain” field and the directory name in the “Path” filed and click on “check sign” (ok) button



**Check statistics of shared hosting website account**

In order to view the stats for your website , please follow the below steps.

- Go to https://www.serverpointapps.com/ , Login to the Client Portal.
- Click on the Menu , then go Web Sites and Stats
- Click on the Stats button 
- It will open a web page with your domain stats.

```diagram

```

**Delete Subwebsite / Domain pointer /Sub domains**

In order to delete the websites you created, please follow the below steps.

- Go to https://www.serverpointapps.com/ , Login to the Client Portal.
- Click on the Menu , then go Web Sites and Stats
- Click on the Delete button which is near the website you want to delete.
